{"lemma":"رُخُّ","slug":"رُخُّ","root":"ر.خ.خ","root_slug":"ر-خ-خ","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-خ-خ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15110","n15113","n15114"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dilute, to mix with water"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to break or crush so as to make soft"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"light shower","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of رَخَّ (raḵḵa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"soft, relaxed, irresolute"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"castle, rook"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"roc (mythical bird)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Classical Persian رُخ (rux)."},"ipa":["/rax.xa/","/raxx/","/ruxx/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15110","headword_ar":"رَخَّ","root":"rx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rax~u","text_ar":"رَخُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of dough,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It had in it much water"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it was soft:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see also 8]. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rax~ahu","text_ar":"رَخَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, T, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) inf. n. as above, (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He broke it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"crushed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so made it soft:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he trod upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and so made it soft."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, K) what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or wine, or beverage: (S, K:) and likewise food with condiment. (JK.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","T","K","TK","S"]},{"entry_id":"n15113","headword_ar":"رَخٌّ","root":"rx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lax,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flaccid:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Golius, on the authority or Meyd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see its fem.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rax~apN","text_ar":"رَخَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaAxN","text_ar":"رَخَاخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n15114","headword_ar":"رُخٌّ","root":"rx","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain soft, flaccid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fragile, plant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaAxN","text_ar":"رَخَاخٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, (mentioned by ISd,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rixaAxN","text_ar":"رِخَاخٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (So in the JK.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain great bird, that carries off the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karokad~an","text_ar":"كَرْكَدَّن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rhinoceros"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K. [See note 22 to ch. xx. of my translation of the “ Thousand and One Nights. ” The word is of Persian origin, arabicized; as it is said to be by Lth in the sense next following.]) ―         -b2-  And hence, as being likened thereto, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One of the pieces with which the game of chess is played;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[called by us the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rook, castle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tower:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rixaxapN","text_ar":"رِخَخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rixaAxN","text_ar":"رِخَاخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, A,) or both. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","JK","A"]}]}}